Dear Hiring Team, 

It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the *Software Engineer* position with *Applied Medical*. I bring over three years of professional experience in full-stack web applications, back-end services, and modern JavaScript frameworks, along with a strong academic foundation as a Master of Science in Computer Science graduate from Pace University, NY.

