I have always been passionate about innovation and improving the accessibility of high-quality technology, and I envision myself contributing my talent to the furthering of Applied Medical's mission to develop innovative products that improve patient outcomes and enable the advancement of minimally invasive surgery. I would love to discuss my interest in this position with your team and can be reached at #ph or #eml. Thank you for your time and consideration, I look forward to connecting!

